&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;font-claude-response-body&quot;&gt;This is a senior IC role with a broad scope and high autonomy. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;font-claude-response-body&quot;&gt;You&#39;ll&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;font-claude-response-body&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;set multi-year direction for the AI recruiting product area, partner with executives on company strategy, influence the work of other PMs, and drive the most ambitious bets in the portfolio.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;font-claude-response-body&quot;&gt;You&#39;ll&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;font-claude-response-body&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;work across product, engineering, design, research, and go-to-market to ship products that meaningfully change how&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;font-claude-response-body&quot;&gt;recruiters&lt;/span&gt;&lt;s
